## Test Commands
 
```bash
# Backend ŌĆö all optimizer unit tests (must stay 29/29)
pytest tests/test_optimizers.py -v
 
# Backend ŌĆö API integration tests
pytest tests/test_api_integration_updated.py -v
 
# Backend ŌĆö all tests
pytest tests/ -x -q
 
# Backend ŌĆö quick smoke test
python -c "from api import app; print('API imports OK')"
 
# Frontend ŌĆö build check (must produce 0 errors)
cd frontend && npm run build
 
# Frontend ŌĆö dev server (requires backend on :5000)
cd frontend && npm start
```
 
