## Frontend Common Tasks (quick reference)
 
Full detail in `references/ui-design.md` and `references/frontend-guide.md`.
 
### Update objective dropdown
See `references/frontend-guide.md` ┬¦ "Objective dropdown options".
Fetch live from `/api/config/objectives` on mount. Fall back to the hardcoded
`OBJECTIVE_OPTIONS` list if fetch fails.
 
### Add K_screen / K_select inputs for hybrid
Show only when `objective === 'hybrid'` or `objective === 'qubo_sa'`.
Both are integer inputs, range 2ŌĆō20. Default: `null` (auto). Pass as
`K_screen` / `K_select` in the optimize payload.
 
### Fix ESLint warnings in CustomizableQuantumDashboard.js
Run `cd frontend && npx eslint src/CustomizableQuantumDashboard.js`.
Common issues: unused state variables (`omega`, `evolutionTime`), missing
`useCallback` deps, stray `console.log` calls.
 
### Make a section more responsive
Use CSS Grid with `grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr))`.
Avoid hardcoded pixel widths. See `references/ui-design.md` ┬¦ "Responsive grid".